{"tid":579738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真定假 新移民一家九人到港3個月成功申請水泉澳大單位公屋","createTime":"2018-03-04T00:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T07:23:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":37,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0aacf83c11561e437499c1a4d0470651efb36e64","tid":579738,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"對於今次被揭露他們一家九口擠住在一個220平方呎的斗室中，陳伯兒子表示無悔，「鬼叫仔女鍾意香港生活咩！」他說，妻兒在鄉間擁有一幢兩層高的磚屋，每層有300多平方呎，居住環境肯定比香港好，不過他們亦並非在全不知情下來港；因為妻子和子女們去年都曾經來過香港「視察環境」，並在現時所住的單位住過一個月，17歲孫女說：「香港好開心，始終好過大陸。」陳伯兒子更說，申請妻兒來港，主要是希望子女可以在香港接受較佳的育，其15歲兒子亦承認爺爺家中的確很擠迫，有時晚上起床都怕吵醒其他人，但他仍然喜歡香港，父親得知可以成功優先到水泉澳大單位公屋，更說非常感謝香港政府，改善一家人居住環境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.funhk.orgs.one/show/144599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.funhk.orgs.one%2Fshow%2F144599&d=sOENwHjyvEI3yH8occPVRrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=221a7f2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.funhk.orgs.one/show/144599</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wongka.orgs.one/images/image/78/7887928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wongka.orgs.one%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F78%2F7887928.jpg&h=aa4ee6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見香討屌到上太空，依單野真定假新聞"},{"pid":"6016eaf1d750634e9a14601abada80e2b7196a35","tid":579738,"uid":155732,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:56:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">妻兒在鄉間擁有一幢兩層高的磚屋</span><br />\n有曬證據都唔捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fb360da0e2532281dbc7b4afbc33a9a52932ef","tid":579738,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:57:03.000Z","msg":"要睇佢點申請喎，<br />\n但水泉澳邨應該冇九人大單位"},{"pid":"c3a1ca98f66fe5aa1f4b77967272552b6e549379","tid":579738,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6fb360da0e2532281dbc7b4afbc33a9a52932ef","tid":579738,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep